In 2016, according to world Health Organization more than 1.9 billion adults, 18 years and older were overweight and 650 million were of obese. Vinnd is a decentralized digital healthcare platform helps to test your blood with the help of express blood test. You need to place an order for portable express blood test kit and you can perform your test by sitting at your home helps you to avoid going to the hospital. Vinnd is designed for each and every individual and diets are based on the blood test results. A drop of blood may reveal what kind of the products would affect your metabolism.  Enter results to vinnd mobile or web app Vinnd intelligent Database will evaluate your results. Users will get your personal diet and recipes that help you in reducing the weight. Instead of going to the doctor and ask for suggestions you can sit in the home and can reduce your weight easily. Projects have several monetization channels that can be the monthly subscription for weight loss program, subscription for health care that provides and retail of express blood test kit and you can even find test stripes helps you in weight loss
